    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I'm a high school history teacher and I'm trying to put together some lecture notes for my students. I want to explain what \"substantive due process\" is, but I'd like the focus to be specifically on how it has been a tool for protecting civil rights and personal liberties. Can you draft an explanation for me that hits those points?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
